ed="T" n="0875b26"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0875b26"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000013606"><placeName>東陽</placeName><placeName>清泰寺</placeName></placeName><persName key="A009605">玄朗</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0875b27"/><persName key="A009605">釋玄朗</persName>，字<persName key="A009605">慧明</persName>，姓<name>傅</name>氏。其先浦陽郡<ptr target="#n3195"/>，<placeName key="PL000000026544">江夏</placeName>太<lb
ed="T" n="0875b28"/>守<persName key="A013673">拯<roleName>公</roleName></persName>之後<ptr target="#n706"/>。<date from-iso="+0220-12-10" key="j18017571823449" to-iso="+0280-05-01"><name>曹魏</name>世</date>，避地于<placeName key="PL000000000197">江左</placeName>，則<placeName key="PL000000000138">梁</placeName>大士<lb
ed="T" n="0875b29"/><persName key="A006833">翕</persName>之六代孫，遂為<placeName key="PL000000013594">烏傷</placeName>人也。母<persName key="A019479">葛<roleName>氏</roleName></persName>初妊，夢<pb ed="T" n="0875c" xml:id="T50.2061.0875c"/><lb
ed="T" n="0875c01"/><anchor xml:id="beg0875sgsz9"/>乘<anchor xml:id="end0875sgsz9"/>羊車飛空躡虛而覺身重。自茲已後，葷<lb
ed="T" n="0875c02"/>血惡聞。殆乎產蓐<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2097"/>，亦如初寐。覺後心輕體<lb
ed="T" n="0875c03"/>安，嬰兒不啼，<anchor xml:id="beg0875004"/>唍<anchor xml:id="end0875004"/>爾而笑。<date from-iso="+0681-01-28" key="j19698181970201" to-iso="+0682-02-15">九歲</date>出家，師授其<lb
ed="T" n="0875c04"/>經，日過七紙。<date key="j19740001974000" when-iso="+0692-07-11"><name>如意</name>元年閏五月十九日</date>，勅度<lb
ed="T" n="0875c05"/>配<placeName key="PL000000013606">清泰寺</placeName>。<date key="j19737751974158" from-iso="+0691-11-29" to-iso="+0692-12-16">弱冠</date>，遠尋<placeName key="PL000000025908">光州</placeName><persName key="A008876">岸<roleName>律師</roleName></persName>，受滿足<lb
ed="T" n="0875c06"/>戒<ptr type="glossary" target="#g33"/>。旋學律範。又博覽經論，搜求異同，<anchor xml:id="beg0875sgsz11"/>尤<anchor xml:id="end0875sgsz11"/>切<lb
ed="T" n="0875c07"/>《<anchor xml:id="beg0875005"/>涅槃<anchor xml:id="end0875005"/>》。<anchor xml:id="beg0875sgsz13"/>常<anchor xml:id="end0875sgsz13"/>恨古人雖有章疏，判斷未為平<lb
ed="T" n="0875c08"/>允。往在<placeName key="PL000000013294"><placeName>會稽</placeName><placeName>妙喜寺</placeName></placeName>與<persName key="A009251">印宗<roleName>禪師</roleName></persName>商<anchor xml:id="beg0875006"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>確</sic><corr>搉</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0875006"/>祕<lb
ed="T" n="0875c09"/>要，雖互相述許，大旨未周。聞<name>天台</name>一宗可<lb
ed="T" n="0875c10"/>以清眾滯，可以趣一理，因詣<placeName key="PL000000014766"><placeName>東陽</placeName><placeName>天宮寺</placeName></placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0875c11"/><persName key="A009596">慧威<roleName>法師</roleName></persName>。<persName key="A009596">威</persName>稟承<placeName key="PL000000014935">括州</placeName><persName key="A001263">智威</persName>──時傳<persName key="A001263">威</persName>是<persName key="A004803">徐陵</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0875c12"/>後身<ptr target="#n3194"/>，<persName key="A004896">灌頂<roleName>師</roleName></persName>之高足也。<persName key="A009605">朗</persName>親附<ref type="person" target="#A009596">之</ref><ptr target="#n3196"/>，不患貧<lb
ed="T" n="0875c13"/>苦。達《法華》、《淨名》<ptr target="#n1177"/>、《大論》<ptr target="#n55"/>、《止觀》<ptr target="#n1173"/>、《禪門》<ptr target="#n2217"/>等，凡一宗之<lb
ed="T" n="0875c14"/>教迹，研覈至精。後依<persName key="A013674">恭<roleName>禪師</roleName></persName>重修觀法，博<lb
ed="T" n="0875c15"/>達<name>儒</name>書，兼閑<name>道</name>宗，無不該覽。雖通諸見，<lb
ed="T" n="0875c16"/>獨以「止觀<ptr type="glossary" target="#g187"/>」以為入道之程，作安心之域。雖<lb
ed="T" n="0875c17"/>眾聖繼想，而以<persName key="A002803">觀音</persName>悲智為事行良津，遊<lb
ed="T" n="0875c18"/>心十乘<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1035"/>，諦冥三觀<ptr type="glossary" target="#g393"/>，四悉<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2098"/>利物，六即<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1286"/>體<anchor xml:id="beg0875007"/>徧<anchor xml:id="end0875007"/>。雖<lb
ed="T" n="0875c19"/>致心物表，身厭人寰，<anchor xml:id="beg0875sgsz15"/>情<anchor xml:id="end0875sgsz15"/>捐舊廬，志栖林<lb
ed="T" n="0875c20"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic><g ref="#Z1249"/></sic><corr>壑</corr></choice>。唯十八種<supplied resp="sgsz">物</supplied><ptr target="#n2425"/>，十二頭陀<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1829"/>，隱<placeName key="PL000000013555">左溪巖</placeName>，因以為<lb
ed="T" n="0875c21"/>號。獨坐一室，三十餘秋，麻紵<ptr type="glossary" target="#g141"/>為衣，糲<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2099"/>蔬充<lb
ed="T" n="0875c22"/>食。有願生<placeName key="PL000000055446">兜率宮</placeName>，必資福事，乃構殿壁，<lb
ed="T" n="0875c23"/>繢<persName key="A002803">觀音</persName>、<persName key="A006023">賓頭盧</persName>像。乃焚香斂念，便感五色<lb
ed="T" n="0875c24"/>神光，道俗俱瞻<ptr target="#n3197"/>，<anchor xml:id="beg0875sgsz17"/>歎<anchor xml:id="end0875sgsz17"/>未曾有。此後或猿玃<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2100"/>來而<lb
ed="T" n="0875c25"/>捧鉢，或飛鳥息以聽經。時有盲狗來至山<lb
ed="T" n="0875c26"/>門，長嘷宛轉于地，<persName key="A009605">朗</persName>憫之，焚香精誠，為狗<lb
ed="T" n="0875c27"/>懺悔，不踰旬日，雙目豁明。至<date from-iso="+0728-02-19" key="j19870051987358" to-iso="+0729-02-06"><name>開元</name>十六年</date>，<lb
ed="T" n="0875c28"/>刺史<persName key="A019480">王上客</persName>屈<persName key="A009605">朗</persName>出山，暫居城下。<persName key="A009605">朗</persName>辭疾，<lb
ed="T" n="0875c29"/>仍歸本居<ptr target="#n3198"/>。厥後誨人匪倦<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1342"/>，講不待<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2101"/>眾。一欝<pb ed="T" n="0876a" xml:id="T50.2061.0876a"/><lb
ed="T" n="0876a01"/>多羅<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1334"/>四十餘年，一尼師壇<ptr type="glossary" target="#g401"/>終身不易。食無<lb
ed="T" n="0876a02"/>重味，居必偏廈<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2102"/>。非因尋經典，不<anchor xml:id="beg0876sgsz1"/>然<anchor xml:id="end0876sgsz1"/>一燭；<lb
ed="T" n="0876a03"/>非因覲聖容，不行一步。其細行修心，蓋徇<lb
ed="T" n="0876a04"/>律法之制，遂得遠域沙門、隣境耆耋<ptr type="glossary" target="#g874"/>擁室填<lb
ed="T" n="0876a05"/>門，若冬陽夏陰，弗召而自至也<ptr target="#n3204"/>。其寺宇凋<lb
ed="T" n="0876a06"/>弊，乃指授僧<persName key="A024757">靈稟</persName>建其殿宇形像<ptr target="#n3199"/>，累二甎<lb
ed="T" n="0876a07"/>塔。繢<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g794"/>事不用牛膠，悉調香汁。<name>天台</name>之教鼎<lb
ed="T" n="0876a08"/>盛，何莫由斯也？一日，顧謂門人曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A009605">吾</ref>眾事<lb
ed="T" n="0876a09"/>云畢，年旦暮焉！」以<date key="j19967381996738" when-iso="+0754-10-13"><name>天寶</name>十三年九月十九日</date><lb
ed="T" n="0876a10"/>薄疾而終，春秋八十有二，僧夏六十一<ptr target="#n3200"/>。置塔<lb
ed="T" n="0876a11"/>於巖所，生常<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2103"/>撰《法華經科文》二卷。付法弟子<lb
ed="T" n="0876a12"/><placeName key="PL000000013647"><placeName>衢州</placeName><placeName>龍丘寺</placeName></placeName><ptr target="#n3201"/><persName key="A013675">道賓</persName>、<placeName key="PL000000013648">淨安寺</placeName><persName key="A011054">慧從</persName>、<placeName key="PL000000013292"><placeName>越州</placeName><placeName>法華寺</placeName></placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0876a13"/><persName key="A013676">法源</persName>、<persName key="A009615">神邕</persName><ptr target="#n3202"/>、<placeName key="PL000000009715"><placeName>常州</placeName><placeName>福業寺</placeName></placeName><persName key="A013677">守真</persName>、<placeName key="PL000000009882"><placeName>蘇州</placeName><placeName>報恩寺</placeName></placeName><persName key="A013678">道<lb
ed="T" n="0876a14"/>遵</persName>、<placeName key="PL000000012466"><placeName>明州</placeName><placeName>大寶寺</placeName></placeName><persName key="A013679">道原</persName>、<placeName key="PL000000013504"><placeName>婺州</placeName><placeName>開元寺</placeName></placeName><persName key="A013680">清辯</persName>。「齠年<lb
ed="T" n="0876a15"/><anchor xml:id="beg0876sgsz3"/>慕<anchor xml:id="end0876sgsz3"/>道，志意求師；不踰三年，思過半<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1565"/>矣！行其<lb
ed="T" n="0876a16"/>道者，號<persName key="A009605">左溪</persName>焉！第其傳法，號<persName key="A009605">五祖</persName>矣<ptr target="#n3203"/>！」<placeName key="PL000000013204">禹<lb
ed="T" n="0876a17"/>山</placeName>沙門<persName key="A010999">神逈</persName>著乎真讚矣！</p><p><lb
ed="T" n="0876a18"/>系曰：觀其<date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date>世已上，求戒者得自選名德<lb
ed="T" n="0876a19"/>為師。近代官度，以引次排之，立司存<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2104"/>主<lb
ed="T" n="0876a20"/>之，不由<anchor xml:id="beg0876sgsz5"/>己<anchor xml:id="end0876sgsz5"/>也。<persName key="A009605">朗</persName>之求戒，不其是乎？如是<lb
ed="T" n="0876a21"/>師資相練<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2105"/>，恩義所生；脫<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2106"/>臨事請為，則喻同<lb
ed="T" n="0876a22"/>野馬<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2107"/>也。</p>
